G1, Gk are the capacitor or inductor element values.
fH, the 3 dB frequency is calculated with: formula_96

The coefficients &quot;A&quot;, &quot;γ&quot;, &quot;β&quot;, &quot;A&quot;&quot;k&quot;, and &quot;B&quot;&quot;k&quot; may be calculated from the following equations:

:formula_97

